# Week 1: Data Acquisition & Cleaning

## Objective

To collect and prepare financial market data for portfolio analysis.

## Data Collection

* Used `yfinance` API to download historical stock data
* Selected 10 diversified stocks across sectors + S&P 500 index

## Data Processing

* Extracted closing prices from raw dataset
* Handled missing values using forward fill method
* Removed remaining null values to ensure clean dataset

## Data Structure

* MultiIndex dataset (Price Type, Ticker)
* Converted into clean format for analysis

## Tools Used

* Python
* Pandas
* yfinance

## Output

* Raw dataset (`raw_stock_data.csv`)
* Cleaned dataset (`cleaned_stock_data.csv`)

## Outcome

Prepared a reliable financial dataset ready for quantitative analysis and modeling.
